            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The reference is to a form of <hi rend="italic">Lychnis dioica</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Silene dioica</hi>) that Becker believed to be a new variety (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4170.xml" resp="#automat">letter from L. E. Becker, 18 May 1863</ref> and n. 1).</note>
